Level = enum
  lvlAll, lvlDebug, lvlInfo, lvlNotice, lvlWarn, lvlError, lvlFatal, lvlNone
LogType = enum
  lkAction, lkValue, lkInformation
LogActKind = enum
  lakStarted, lakOngoing, lakStopped

Log = object
  logPos*: LogPos
  format*: LogFormat
  case kind*: LogType
  of lkValue:
      key*: string
      value*: JsonNode

  of lkInformation:
      level*: Level

  of lkAction:
      actKind*: LogActionKind
